invalid type: string "Violations may result in disciplinary action.\n\n---\n\n# 19. Investigations\n\nThe company may investigate suspected violations of policies, laws, or ethical standards.\n\nEmployees are expected to cooperate honestly with investigations.\n\nFailure to cooperate may result in disciplinary action.\n\n---\n\n# 20. Disciplinary Action\n\nmpany assets and use them responsibly.\n=